tictactoeCLI

A simple Tic Tac Toe command line game application.

To run:
1. type this on your terminal "php tictactoe.php".

Gameplay:
a. The board is numbered 1-9
|| 7 | 8 | 9 ||
---------------
|| 4 | 5 | 6 ||
---------------
|| 1 | 2 | 3 ||
b. Select your letter (X or O)
c. The computer will select randomly who will go first.
d. Press the number where you want to put X or O.
e. Wait for computer's turn and make your move.
f. Repeat d and e until a winner is declared.
